#. Tag: para
#: Configuration.xml:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"SECURITY RISK! To avoid a security risk, you MUST specify the value of the "
"attribute SuckerPassword in the Server Peer config (messaging-service.xml). "
"If you do not specify a value, the default value will be used. Any person "
"that knows the default value will be able to access to all destinations on "
"the server. The password chosen should only be exposed to administrators"
msgstr ""
"安全风险！要避免安全风险，你必须指定 Server Peer 配置文件（messaging-service."
"xml）里的 SuckerPassword 属性的值。如果你没有进行指定，缺省值将被使用。任何知"
"道缺省值的人都可以访问服务器上的所有目的地。只有管理员才应该知道这个密码。"

#. Tag: title
#: Configuration.xml:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "ServerPeer attributes"
msgstr "ServerPeer 的属性"

#. Tag: para
